Titolo: My Horse Prince

Anno: 2016

Descrizione: My Horse Prince (うまのプリンスさま, Uma no Prince-Sama) is a 2016 Japanese Otome game for mobile devices. It was developed by USAYA and was released in Japanese during November 2016 and in English the following month, both for iOS and Android. The game's story follows a young woman who finds herself taking ownership of — and reluctantly falling in love with — a horse with a human face.

Genere: Otome game

Valutazione: N/A
